  "original_title": "\u0dba\u0ddd\u0da2\u0db1\u0dcf \u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0db1\u0db8\u0dca \u0dad\u0dd4\u0db1\u0db8 \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0db1\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "All three suggested names are accepted",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Parliamentary Secretary General Dhammika Dasanayake officially announced to Parliament that three names have been proposed for the post of President.",
        "The General Secretary said that the names of Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe, Dallas Alahaperuma and Mr. Anura Dissanayake have been suggested and he will accept those names."
      ],
